{"title":"父亲土地和我","authors":["胡晓靖"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲土地和我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡晓靖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我接下了你修补了一生的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一方土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就要走在你垒起的田埂上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛着你用过的犁耙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让勤恳像禾苗一样长满田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会渐渐地溶入你的背影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把一生的愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都种在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把背脊弓成不朽的苍穹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让粗重的呼吸降下一阵阵甜雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是你土地里长出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最饱满的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用手为我除草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用话语为我施肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你种植的星星和月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂养了我无邪的童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每一个春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都把我小小的年纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插上了梦的柳笛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年秋天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于有一封《大学录取通知书》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞落于你的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你送我到遥远的车站"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才第一次看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天已飘落在你的头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放心吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我接下了这方土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要把它揣在心间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带到喧闹的城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄掉它顽固的硗薄和贫瘠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要用知识作鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以科学为犁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}